{"TopicId":36137,"ForumId":18,"TopicTitle":"What\u0026#039;s your favourite \u0026quot;old\u0026quot; game?","CreatedByName":"joppiesaus","CreatedById":57698,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-07-06T18:27:12Z","PageNum":2,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"segaprophet","CreatedById":14087,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-07-07T18:12:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003Ememories..\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://janaiblog.files.wordpress.com/2010/05/som_boss1.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022som_boss1.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Pachi3080","CreatedById":65427,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-07-07T18:28:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EC\u0026amp;C tiberian sun\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Seelenamt","CreatedById":71478,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-07-07T22:04:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-01-08T00:32:24Z\u0022 title=\u002201/08/2020 12:32  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003EJanuary 8, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by Seelenamt\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\u200B\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"nhnifong","CreatedById":12196,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-07-07T22:27:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EThe only thing I\u0027ll boot up an old Windows install for is Roller Coaster Tycoon or Sim City 2.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI\u0027ll occationally go back and play Ocarina of Time too.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EAs for the not-so-old games, I have a lot of find memories playing Halo with my sister, and I would love to get another game of halo going with her again, possibly at thanksgiving, but it would involve several hours of fiddling around with software to get it working because I no longer have an XBOX.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EAnd for the extra old games, Go takes the cake. It\u0027s almost 2600 years old!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"7499275","CreatedById":70640,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-07-08T04:14:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EGood old sim city 4! Came out in 2003 I believe, actually not only do I play but I have made several mods myself for it! \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"jwenting","CreatedById":57735,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-07-08T09:03:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Pachi3080\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Pachi3080\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EC\u0026amp;C tiberian sun\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003Enow that one was good. If you liked it, you\u0027d also have liked Total Annihilation.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Total_Annihilation\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Total_Annihilation\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Canopus","CreatedById":57774,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-07-08T13:59:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003Ei too love both Star Wars Battlefront games.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EMy favourite old game is Ascendancy. Its a great 4X game with turnbased spacebattles and strange Alien Races\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://www.abload.de/img/ascendancy-races81kkg.png\u0022 alt=\u0022ascendancy-races81kkg.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://www.mobygames.com/images/shots/l/494005-ascendancy-dos-screenshot-the-map-can-be-rotated-and-zoomed.png\u0022 alt=\u0022494005-ascendancy-dos-screenshot-the-map-can-be-rotated-and-zoomed.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://www.abandonia.com/files/games/221/Ascendancy_7.png\u0022 alt=\u0022Ascendancy_7.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EIt had 3 Dimensional Star systems and Starmaps and a great soundtrack.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://m.youtube.com/#/watch?v=RXm6DL3D4Ws\u0026amp;desktop_uri=%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DRXm6DL3D4Ws\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://m.youtube.com/#/watch?v=RXm6DL3D4Ws\u0026amp;desktop_uri=%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DRXm6DL3D4Ws\u003C/a\u003E \u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222013-07-08T14:15:20Z\u0022 title=\u002207/08/2013 02:15  PM\u0022 data-short=\u002211 yr\u0022\u003EJuly 8, 2013\u003C/time\u003E by Canopus\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"nhnifong","CreatedById":12196,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-07-08T14:21:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI tried to learn Ascendancy once. It\u0027s very complicated.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Canopus","CreatedById":57774,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-07-08T16:14:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022nhnifong\u0022 data-cite=\u0022nhnifong\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EI tried to learn Ascendancy once. It\u0027s very complicated.\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003EIt is hard at first but once you get the idea it is a great game. i even prefer it over Masters of Orion.\n"},{"CreatedByName":"General Rarity","CreatedById":67829,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-07-09T00:32:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EEvery game in Command and Conquer, The First Decade. I also like the early versions of Trainz railroad sim.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Spartwo","CreatedById":58131,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-07-09T00:44:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003Ebest..game...EVAR!!\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://www.darkspyro.net/spyrothedragon/images/cover_us_large.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022cover_us_large.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EIt introduced me to gaming(In 2003 though)\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Grove","CreatedById":5188,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-07-09T01:01:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EGrand Theft Auto San Andreas and Vice City. And Sim City 4 of course.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"nyrath","CreatedById":61886,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-07-09T01:02:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EOgre\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i816.photobucket.com/albums/zz85/winchellchung/VisorOgre3.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022VisorOgre3.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i816.photobucket.com/albums/zz85/winchellchung/PocketOgre.png\u0022 alt=\u0022PocketOgre.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EWarpWar\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i816.photobucket.com/albums/zz85/winchellchung/WarpWarScreenCap001.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022WarpWarScreenCap001.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ETriplanetary\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i816.photobucket.com/albums/zz85/winchellchung/tripyWIP14.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022tripyWIP14.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EHomeworlds\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i816.photobucket.com/albums/zz85/winchellchung/Homeworlds19.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022Homeworlds19.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Destroyer","CreatedById":36109,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-07-09T01:27:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022the destroyer\u0022 data-cite=\u0022the destroyer\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003Ehmmm.\u003Cp\u003EI\u0027d say baris.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EOr roller coaster tycoon 2. I played it for years.\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003ECorrection!\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EMotorcross Madness!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Tremzack","CreatedById":27768,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-07-09T02:34:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EAhh, my favorite would have to be the first Ratchet and Clank, in 2002\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"AntonioAJC","CreatedById":16486,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-07-09T03:41:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EHalo Combat Evolved ^.^\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EOne of the first FPS games I\u0027ve played that I spent years playing.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Capt.Joseph Kerbertson","CreatedById":57354,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-07-09T13:55:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EMechwarrior 3 coupled with my sidewinder force feedback joystick... sweetness.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EMe and the guys at my fire station had delta force land warrior set up on lan... 16 fire fighters after hours going at it... hilarity ensued every shift.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Xeldrak","CreatedById":57228,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-07-09T14:01:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EThats easy: X-Com: Enemy Unknown\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ENot, not this one...\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://blogs-images.forbes.com/jasonevangelho/files/2012/10/XCOM_Enemy_Unknown_Game_Cover.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022XCOM_Enemy_Unknown_Game_Cover.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThis one!\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022https://2.bp.blogspot.com/_ZNKkeiOrZCc/S8WhHMCmuXI/AAAAAAAAAG0/QjLdvJbRQtA/s400/ufo3.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022ufo3.gif\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EOh, how many nights have I spent defending Earth from these aliens?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MalletFace","CreatedById":62341,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-07-09T14:35:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI have seen many titles I still play every single day in this thread. There is Age of Empires II, Command and Conquer, Roller Coaster Tycoon, And Battlefield 1942.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EIf I had to pick one game from way back when, it would have to be Command and Conquer: Red Alert 2, and its expansion. The campaigns\u0027 stories were extra cheesy, and the game looked like you were playing with toys, but that is the game I have probably loved the most. \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ESeeing the name of this game mentioned anywhere outside of a Command and Conquer forum also makes me a little happy, especially when a picture of Yuri himself pops up.\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222013-07-09T14:52:27Z\u0022 title=\u002207/09/2013 02:52  PM\u0022 data-short=\u002211 yr\u0022\u003EJuly 9, 2013\u003C/time\u003E by MalletFace\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Awaras","CreatedById":15671,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-07-09T16:09:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Canopus\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Canopus\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003Ei too love both Star Wars Battlefront games.\u003Cp\u003EMy favourite old game is Ascendancy. Its a great 4X game with turnbased spacebattles and strange Alien Races\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E*snip*\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EIt had 3 Dimensional Star systems and Starmaps and a great soundtrack.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E*snip*\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EAscendancy was a great game, but my god, the colony micromanagement... @_@\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222013-07-09T16:11:45Z\u0022 title=\u002207/09/2013 04:11  PM\u0022 data-short=\u002211 yr\u0022\u003EJuly 9, 2013\u003C/time\u003E by Awaras\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Canopus","CreatedById":57774,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-07-09T21:42:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Awaras\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Awaras\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EAscendancy was a great game, but my god, the colony micromanagement... @_@\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003EYes very complicated \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E I heard that they are currently making a sequel though.\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Rosco P. Coltrane","CreatedById":61065,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-07-10T02:46:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ERed Baron II/3D from 1997, probably the fest flight sim I know. Man I played that game sooooo much. Too bad I can\u0027t make it work with a modern PC.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://www.wingsofhonour.com/redbaron3d/img_redbaron3d_pc-box-cover_424x500x24b.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022img_redbaron3d_pc-box-cover_424x500x24b.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EAnd Age Of Empires II, I still play it on a regular basis.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mr. Pseudonym","CreatedById":27614,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-07-10T13:25:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ELego racers. Hands down the best racing game ever. Seriously.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/alWSLse.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022alWSLse.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Awaras","CreatedById":15671,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-07-10T13:37:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EBesides the original XCOM, the two games that I have sunk by far the most time in are Elite II: Frontier and Master of Orion II. \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EKSP is the only game that came close to these classics in recent years in my mind...\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Felsmak","CreatedById":27187,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-07-10T13:41:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Mr. Pseudonym\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Mr. Pseudonym\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003ELego racers. Hands down the best racing game ever. Seriously.\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI always wanted to play it, but could never get it to work. \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_sad.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:(\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}